    <monitor x="10" precision="0" y="370" height="45" fontSize="11" display="Litter On Ground" width="190" sizeVersion="0">total-litter-on-ground</monitor>
    <monitor x="10" precision="3" y="420" height="45" fontSize="11" display="Bin Utilization Rate" width="190" sizeVersion="0">bin-utilization-rate</monitor>
    <monitor x="10" precision="0" y="470" height="45" fontSize="11" display="Hotspot Count" width="190" sizeVersion="0">litter-hotspot-count</monitor>
    <plot x="760" autoPlotX="true" yMax="10.0" autoPlotY="true" yAxis="litter" y="10" xMin="0.0" height="200" legend="false" xMax="1000.0" yMin="0.0" xAxis="ticks" display="Litter Over Time" width="300" sizeVersion="0">
      <setup></setup>
      <update></update>
      <pen interval="1.0" mode="0" display="ground litter" color="-2674135" legend="true">
        <setup></setup>
        <update>plot total-litter-on-ground</update>
      </pen>
    </plot>
    <plot x="760" autoPlotX="true" yMax="1.0" autoPlotY="true" yAxis="norm signal" y="220" xMin="0.0" height="200" legend="false" xMax="1000.0" yMin="0.0" xAxis="ticks" display="Norm Signal Over Time" width="300" sizeVersion="0">
      <setup></setup>
      <update></update>
      <pen interval="1.0" mode="0" display="mean norm" color="-13345367" legend="true">
        <setup></setup>
        <update>if any? people [ plot mean [norm-signal-personal] of people ]</update>
      </pen>
    </plot>
    <slider x="17" step="0.01" y="563" max="1" width="250" display="jogger-to-leisurers-ratio" height="50" min="0" direction="Horizontal" default="0.33" variable="jogger-to-leisurers-ratio"></slider>
    <button x="523" y="562" height="40" disableUntilTicks="false" forever="true" kind="Observer" width="91" display="Clear Bins">ask bins [die]</button>
    <button x="412" y="562" height="40" disableUntilTicks="false" forever="true" kind="Observer" width="102" display="Remove bin">remove-bin-mouse</button>
    <button x="319" y="562" height="40" disableUntilTicks="false" forever="true" kind="Observer" width="87" display="Place Bin">place-bin-mouse</button>
  </widgets>
  <info><![CDATA[## WHAT IS IT?

An Agent-Based Model simulating pedestrian littering behavior at Fuente Osmena Circle, Cebu City.
Grounded in Goal Framing Theory (Lindenberg & Steg, 2007).

## HOW TO USE IT

1. Set population-size (20-70)
2. Set initial-litter (0=clean, 5=dirty)
3. Set bin-placement (1=sparse, 2=moderate, 3=dense)
4. Toggle limit-ticks ON for BehaviorSpace runs (stops at 1000 ticks)
5. Click Setup then Go

## ZONES

- Exterior: outside park boundary, non-traversable
- Grass: open park area, highest litter attractiveness
- Outer ring: paved walkway near park edge, joggers run here
- Inner plaza: large paved area around fountain, sitters congregate here
- Fountain: center structure, non-traversable
- Path: diagonal NE-SW connecting path
- Entrance: spawn and exit points at NE and SW
]]></info>
